{"id": 1356, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得什么叫做“真正的休息”？", "description": "什么才能让你真正放松？反正单位举办的“团队建设”活动只会让我更累。（题图来自：Rune Fisker）", "record_count": 6675, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20161130101635R6o03fr74ZGDMaKd.gif", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-12-01T03:00:19Z", "options": [{"id": 138496, "content": "一个人看电影", "image": "img/option/option/201612011258178WT7i4FwQ3qYRkK0.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 742763}, {"id": 138752, "content": "一个人去旅游", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 742305}, {"id": 139008, "content": "静思是最好的休息", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 752207}, {"id": 139776, "content": "还是喜欢去从来没去过的地方走一走", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 799656}, {"id": 138497, "content": "做自己喜欢想做的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 851241}, {"id": 138753, "content": "心无杂念，内心平静", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 605591}, {"id": 139009, "content": "捉急的工作全部搞定的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 853133}, {"id": 139265, "content": "回到最原始的状态，没有手机，和大自然待一天，没有烦恼。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 853819}, {"id": 140033, "content": "在床上完成所有的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 38243}, {"id": 159745, "content": "毫无拘束，最好一觉到天亮", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 919339}, {"id": 138498, "content": "之后精神愉悦、做事有动力", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 461105}, {"id": 138754, "content": "躺着发呆……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 406099}, {"id": 139010, "content": "和喜欢的人一起躺在床上看书说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 703482}, {"id": 140546, "content": "想干什么就干什么，无拘无束", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 854306}, {"id": 138499, "content": "大脑放空，无忧无虑的享受优越的生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 786365}, {"id": 138755, "content": "做喜欢的事儿", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 852728}, {"id": 139011, "content": "工作微信群安静了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1133150}, {"id": 139779, "content": "一个人的时候就很舒服了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 854612}, {"id": 138500, "content": "想玩就玩，想睡就睡。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 807391}, {"id": 139012, "content": "死去", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 779393}, {"id": 139524, "content": "彻底放空脑子不做梦 大字型躺着", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 408949}, {"id": 151812, "content": "吃顿好饭，睡个好觉（ps：自然醒）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 896757}, {"id": 138501, "content": "放下心里包袱的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 370968}, {"id": 139013, "content": "其实工作完，安然喝杯咖啡奶茶酒，看场电影，然后回家一个澡之后马上睡觉，护肤品都不用抹就是休息了。", "image": "img/option/option/20161202064841ds3VxX1TYm4KvfBW", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 550617}, {"id": 142341, "content": "没有手机，就会有真正的休息", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 855906}, {"id": 138502, "content": "安静的时光，有家人陪伴，放松地读自己喜欢的书。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 765447}, {"id": 139014, "content": "有时间及没有其他方面阻力，直到主动想工作为止", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 650443}, {"id": 140550, "content": "没有人打扰，没有人干涉，随意随机安排自己的时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 857980}, {"id": 282374, "content": "我想一段时间的休息就是一段时间的本质自由时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1204679}, {"id": 138503, "content": "自己一个人在家 不用在任何人面前伪装。想干嘛就干嘛。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 807486}, {"id": 139015, "content": "想干嘛干嘛的时候，没人唠叨", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 792592}, {"id": 139271, "content": "没有手机 没有认识的人\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 356358}, {"id": 139527, "content": "随心所欲的放空", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 855076}, {"id": 163335, "content": "轻松的做自己喜欢的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 922043}, {"id": 138504, "content": "音响听歌，冒根儿烟，喝杯酒，窝在沙发里", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 793963}, {"id": 139016, "content": "和自己最爱的人，来一场说走就走的旅行", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 852516}, {"id": 160520, "content": "只要没人跟我说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 502909}, {"id": 138505, "content": "做一些会让我忘掉责任感的事情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 797983}, {"id": 138761, "content": "让我一个人待着", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 839452}, {"id": 139017, "content": "说走就走的旅行", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 853160}, {"id": 139018, "content": "不管做什么，不带手机就ok", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 743127}, {"id": 139530, "content": "真正觉得开心放松，而不是傻笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 855075}, {"id": 139019, "content": "独处，谁也不找你，啥事也没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 766177}, {"id": 166155, "content": "骑着单车窜进各种小巷", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 931752}, {"id": 138764, "content": "一部电影可以看到很晚很晚，也不必担心第二天迟到。早上睡到自然醒，并且可以在床上玩一会手机，好好享受一顿早餐，然后制定一天的计划，去精力充沛地完成。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 272654}, {"id": 139020, "content": "通讯断掉 一个人想干什么干什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 759964}, {"id": 139276, "content": "一个人安安静静地看自己喜欢看的书或电影，并沉迷于其中而忘了外界的存在。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 183041}, {"id": 139021, "content": "自己有思考的颓废", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 849352}, {"id": 138510, "content": "孤独", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 742602}, {"id": 139022, "content": "安静", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 66516}]}